description: I was visiting a friend at a hospital today but I didn't forget to pack my camera. Once the visit was done, I started looking for cute boys outside of the building. It didn't go as I planned, everyone was just too busy or ignoring me. At last I met this young and shy guy Zdenek. He was very sweet and agreed to have a little chat with me. The boy had an innocent look but he was no saint. After all his girlfriend got pregnant when being only 23 years old. That put him into a tough financial situation. He worked as a warehouse worker and took weekend part-time jobs. I was lucky to bump into him, he would normally be at work. I simply couldn't squander this opportunity. Guys like this aren't easy to come by. He took me to his place, where the real fun started. Trust me, the boy was just superb.
title: Czech Hunter 393
